<subSubSection pageId="28" pageNumber="513" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1437,150,393]" pageId="28" pageNumber="513">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,222,248]" pageId="28" pageNumber="513">Remarks.</emphasis>
The diagnosis of the genus is emended mainly because the presence of the accessory flagellum and the gill on the coxa 7 is confirmed in the present study. However, in the papers dealing with the other 
<taxonomicName class="Malacostraca" family="Ochlesidae" genus="Antarctodius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="28" pageNumber="513" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis box="[1293,1437,258,284]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="513">Antarctodius</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
, the accessory flagellum is stated to be absent and the gill is not mentioned (
<bibRefCitation author="Watling, L. &amp; Holman, H." box="[1083,1363,294,320]" pageId="28" pageNumber="513" pagination="181 - 227" refId="ref13421" refString="Watling, L. &amp; Holman, H. (1981) Additional acanthonotozomatid, paramphithoid, and stegocephalid Amphipoda from the Southern Ocean. Proceeding of the Biological Society of Washington, 94, 181 - 227." type="journal article" year="1981">Watling &amp; Holman 1981</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Coleman, C. O. &amp; Kauffeldt, J." pageId="28" pageNumber="513" pagination="427 - 434" refId="ref12758" refString="Coleman, C. O. &amp; Kauffeldt, J. (2001) Antarctodius rauscherti, a new species (Crustacea: Amphipoda: Ochlesidae) from the Antarctic Ocean. Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington, 114, 427 - 434." type="journal article" year="2001">Coleman &amp; Kauffeldt 2001</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Labay, V. S." box="[419,557,330,356]" pageId="28" pageNumber="513" pagination="35 - 44" refId="ref13000" refString="Labay, V. S. (2010) A new species and subspecies of Ochlesidae Stebbing, 1910 (Amphipoda: Gammaridea) from the Okhotsk Sea. Zootaxa, 2354 (1), 35 - 44. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 2354.1.3" type="journal article" year="2010">Labay 2010</bibRefCitation>
). A closer examination of them is needed.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
